(13747,	1036,	'cd_extra_4_cd_extra_copy',	'<a name=\"partners\"></a>\r\n<h2><strong> </strong></h2>\r\nWhen we started making our first film on \"character\" three years ago, <em>The Science of Character</em>, we teamed with countless scientists and educators for research, and searched across the web for resources. We\'ve curated of amazing research and tools, but what we didn\'t find is one place that aggregates all the ideas and resources around character from different perspectives. One hub that brings it all together. We decided to start building one. COMING SOON!\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p>'),
