(487,	9,	'2016-08-03 18:39:48',	'2016-08-03 18:39:48',	'<h1>The Adaptable Mind</h1>\nThe film is available with subtitles in Arabic, Chinese, English captions, French, German, Hebrew, Hindi, Russian, Spanish, and Swahili.\n\nThe Adaptable Mind (11 mins) explores the skills we need to flourish in the 21st Century. It is one of the featured films for this upcoming Character Day on September 22nd, 2016. It was just selected by the US State Department as part of their American Film Showcase<a href=\"#\">,</a> where they send films and filmmakers around the world to represent the US and foster dialogue across borders. The film premiered last year in over 6700 classrooms, schools, and organizations in 41 countries for <a href=\"http://www.letitripple.org/highlights-from-previous-character-days/\">Character Day 2015</a>\n\nWe hope you\'ll join us for <a href=\"http://www.letitripple.org/character-day\">Character Day 2016</a>!\n<h2>Resource Hub</h2>\nDive deeper into these ideas with thousands of resources including lesson plans, discussion guides, research, websites, books, films, and more. Discussion Guides and Lesson Plans for The Adaptable Mind are available. COMING SOON!',	'Adaptable Mind',	'',	'inherit',	'closed',	'closed',	'',	'122-autosave-v1',	'',	'',	'2016-08-03 18:39:48',	'2016-08-03 18:39:48',	'',	122,	'http://www.letitripple.dreamhosters.com/2016/07/22/122-autosave-v1/',	0,	'revision',	'',	0),
