(867,	9,	'2016-08-02 10:53:52',	'2016-08-02 10:53:52',	'<h1 class=\"headline\">Free Speech 50th Anniversary Cloud Film</h1>\r\nOn Oct 1, 1964, on the steps of Sproul Hall at UC Berkeley, powerful voices spoke out and the the Free Speech Movement began. To commemorate the 50th anniversary, we invited people from around the world to read the words of two leaders, Martin Luther King Jr. and Mario Savio...and we made a 2 minute Cloud Film. Thank you everyone who sent in videos and helped make this film possible and to everyone who has participated in the Free Speech Movement over the past 50 years. #FSM50\r\n\r\nWe hope you’ll join us for <a href=\"http://www.letitripple.org/character-day\">Character Day 2016</a>!',	'Free Speech',	'',	'inherit',	'closed',	'closed',	'',	'134-revision-v1',	'',	'',	'2016-08-02 10:53:52',	'2016-08-02 10:53:52',	'',	134,	'http://www.letitripple.org/2016/08/02/134-revision-v1/',	0,	'revision',	'',	0),
(868,	9,	'2016-08-02 11:06:30',	'2016-08-02 11:06:30',	'<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-678\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/letitripple-media/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/24221228/MofaM_Periodic_Table.png\" alt=\"MofaM_Periodic_Table\" width=\"650\" height=\"437\" />\r\n\r\nBuilding on the global success and momentum of Character Day 2015, in which hundreds of thousands participated and viewed the films “The Making of a Mensch” and “The Adaptable Mind,” Emmy-nominated filmmaker Tiffany Shlain’s nonprofit “Let it Ripple” this year will broaden the initiative’s reach that uses film and discussion materials to create a global conversation about the importance of character-building in today’s 24/7 world—developing strengths like creativity, humility, grit, courage, compassion and empathy. Thousands of groups have already signed up to participate in Character Day 2016, set for September 22. Let It Ripple is encouraging groups (schools, organizations, companies, camps, congregations, JCCs, museums, and communities of any size) to sign up—the first 10,000 groups to sign up will receive a free printed discussion package. Watch a just-released one-minute trailer about Character Day and sign up at www.characterday.org.\r\n\r\n<a class=\"buttonA\" href=\"http://jewishlinkbwc.com/index.php?option=com_content&amp;id=7981%3Acharacter-day-2016-poised-to-reach-millions-in-global-conversation&amp;Itemid=584\">Read more here</a>',	'Character Day 2016 Poised to Reach Millions in Global Conversation - The Jewish Link',	'',	'inherit',	'closed',	'closed',	'',	'601-revision-v1',	'',	'',	'2016-08-02 11:06:30',	'2016-08-02 11:06:30',	'',	601,	'http://www.letitripple.org/2016/08/02/601-revision-v1/',	0,	'revision',	'',	0),
