o Opera House - Natural Connection\r\n2000: San Francisco Masonic Theater - Machine Time',	'Awards and Distinctions',	'',	'publish',	'closed',	'closed',	'',	'awards-and-distinctions',	'',	'',	'2016-08-02 11:26:18',	'2016-08-02 11:26:18',	'',	82,	'http://www.letitripple.org/?page_id=873',	0,	'page',	'',	0),
