(914,	9,	'2016-08-02 12:59:48',	'2016-08-02 12:59:48',	'<h1 class=\"headline\">Engage</h1>\r\nOver the course of 6 months, we asked people from all over the world to film themselves feeling their heartbeat and thinking about what it means. This is the film that unfolded… <em>Engage</em> premiered at Interdependence Day 2012, screening live at Interdependence Day events in Los Angeles with Mayor Antonio Villaraigosa’s office. See complete <a href=\"http://www.letitripple.org/films/engage/engage-list-of-credits/\">list of credits and participants</a>.\r\n\r\n<em>Engage</em> has already been translated into many languages including: Swahili, Spanish, French, Chinese, Arabic, Hindi, and Russian. The Let it Ripple films combined have been translated into over 70 languages.\r\n<blockquote>“The difference between what we are doing and what we are capable of doing\r\nwould solve most of the world’s problems.”\r\n<h3><em>Mahatma Gandhi</em></h3>\r\n&nbsp;</blockquote>',	'Engage',	'',	'inherit',	'closed',	'closed',	'',	'130-revision-v1',	'',	'',	'2016-08-02 12:59:48',	'2016-08-02 12:59:48',	'',	130,	'http://www.letitripple.org/2016/08/02/130-revision-v1/',	0,	'revision',	'',	0),
