(967,	9,	'2016-08-02 23:47:03',	'2016-08-02 23:47:03',	'<h1>Get Involved</h1>\r\n<div id=\"content\">\r\n<div id=\"intro\" class=\"intro\">\r\n<div class=\"text-content\">\r\n\r\nJoin the thousands of people who are part of the Let it Ripple project.\r\n\r\n<strong>Submit Video Entries </strong>for the next Cloud Film. We almost always have a call for submissions open. It only takes 2 minutes to be part of the films!\r\n\r\n<strong>Translate </strong>one of the films. The Let it Ripple films have been volunteer translated into nearly 70 languages. We would love your help to make them even more accessible.\r\n\r\n<strong>Host a screening</strong>. Join the growing community of over 26,000 classrooms, schools, and orgs spreading the important conversation about building character and more! For more information about Character Day 2016 <strong><a href=\"http://www.moxieinstitute.org/sign_up\">sign up for our newsletter</a></strong>.\r\n\r\n<strong>Share </strong>the films with your social media community and Let it Ripple!\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>',	'Get Involved',	'',	'inherit',	'closed',	'closed',	'',	'86-revision-v1',	'',	'',	'2016-08-02 23:47:03',	'2016-08-02 23:47:03',	'',	86,	'http://www.letitripple.org/2016/08/02/86-revision-v1/',	0,	'revision',	'',	0),
